{"tid":920942,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"鍾意左個唔應該鍾意既人...","createTime":"2018-11-29T07:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T08:23:01.000Z","uid":219164,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"606c7f0864921d2787d03a24deaa10d0b05fdb87","tid":920942,"uid":219164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:57:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n岩岩識果個女仔既時候已經知佢有男友 識耐左發現佢係我理想型 但我同自己講過佢唔可以係我既target 因為真係唔想好似拆散人地咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到近排發現開始對佢有感覺 成日都想見到佢 見到佢會心跳加速 又夢到佢 就知中左招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我真係唔想做第三者去界入佢地 佢讀多半年可能就會轉校<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我應該等佢定應該點做？<br />\n利申：初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nSorry for 1999"},{"pid":"af5527f4714d83c68648b5f46d231eb2fedcb386","tid":920942,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:58:15.000Z","msg":"等埋單"},{"pid":"24020739e90c322feedc7fb9444a9a85a39038bb","tid":920942,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"中學生就努力讀書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f383c5790f092ed469ab1d06aaca11e9a303eef5","tid":920942,"uid":219164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24020739e90c322feedc7fb9444a9a85a39038bb","tid":920942,"uid":38604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:58:52.000Z","msg":"中學生就努力讀書啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T07:59:59.000Z","msg":"大專<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8642ab21f685a810ed621cd24529b3a576b503f","tid":920942,"uid":126876,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"照下鏡<br />\n應該就知道自己介入咗都影響唔到啲咩"},{"pid":"4351aa7383c5e2a404d4d0335a31d1ff29f28fbb","tid":920942,"uid":224168,"like":1,"dislike":0,